        npcId - Character ID

        race - Character race name
        attitude - NPC attitude name
        trade - True if character is trader(can trade with player)
        train - True if character is trainer(can train player)
        guildID - Character guild ID
        level - Character level

        artifact - Character artifact
        spritesheet - Character sprite sheet file name
        staticAvatar - True if sprite sheet is for static avatar
        portraitName - Character portrait file name
        gold - Character cash
        invItems - List with IDs of all character items
        skills - List with IDs of all character skills
        effects - List with IDs of all characters effects
        professions - List with character professions
        trainings - List with all character trainings
